Examples

library(LFQService)
mb <- LFQServiceData::basicModel_p1807
linfct <- linfct_from_model(mb)
names(linfct)

#> [1] "linfct_factors"      "linfct_interactions"
my_glht(mb, linfct$linfct_factors)
